dcterms:description: The ASSISTments datasets consist of longitudinal data gathered from the ASSISTment platform, an online tutoring service. They feature math exercises from grade school, sourced from the Massachusetts Comprehensive Assessment System (MCAS), encompassing various question types like multiple choice, text, and open-ended questions.
dcterms:title: ASSISTments datasets

dcterms:description: ASSISTments2009 is a specific version of the ASSISTments datasets, collected during the 2009-2010 school year, initially containing 525,535 interactions, including duplicates.
dcterms:title: ASSISTments2009
